Doubloon - lucky charm
------------------------------------------------------------
Lore is filled with stories surrounding charms, trinkets,
and jewelry that Swashbucklers would carry into battle.
Though these varied, one repeated motif is the "lucky"
doubloon. Though no one could ever prove these coins
provided any real protection, Swashbucklers continue to
carry them when possible. 

With this ability, a Swashbuckler can offer up some of their
own booty to temporarily receive the buff of the golden
doubloon. While active, a Swashbuckler may find they get
the most out of their armour.

GL: 11
SP: 25
command:  doubloon
duration: medium
